<i>noun</i>: 채색 [채ː색 ], 착색 [착쌕], 색칠 [색칠] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>채색 [채ː색 ]</dt><br>
<dd>1. variegated colors</dd><br>
<dd>여러 가지 고운 빛깔.</dd><br>
<dd>Different fair colors.</dd><br>
<dd>2. coloring</dd><br>
<dd>그림 등에 색을 칠함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of applying color to a painting, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>3. color paint</dd><br>
<dd>색을 칠하는 데에 쓰는 물감.</dd><br>
<dd>A paint used to apply color.</dd><br>
<dt>착색 [착쌕]</dt><br>
<dd>coloring; tinting</dd><br>
<dd>물을 들이거나 색을 칠해서 빛깔이 나게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of dyeing or coloring something to give it a certain color.</dd><br>
<dt>색칠 [색칠]</dt><br>
<dd>coloring; painting</dd><br>
<dd>색깔이 나도록 칠을 함. 또는 그 칠.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of painting something in order to have a color, or the coloring.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>